<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="after-adv">after <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɑːftə(r)/    美 /'æftər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>后来；以后</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the day after 
第二天；次日</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He came here on Monday and left three days after(=three days later/after three days).
他星期一来到这里，三天后就走了。</p></div></div>